# version : 0.1
# date : 08 August 2018
# Get the current value of a given configuration field (may be empty if field does not exist or is not set)

### Usage
# ./GetConfField <file> <field>

### Exit Code
#
# 0 : Command successfull
# 1 : Wrong Number of argument
# 2 : Requisted file does not exist or is empty
#

